---
title: Asian Chicken Tacos & Crispy Shallots for Dinner with Asian Chicken Salad & Sesame Dressing for Lunch
description: Cook once, with a twist for lunch. Cook an amazing dinner as usual then create a new twist on the recipe to create something different for lunch the next day! First, you’ll have tasty Asian chicken tacos with a crisp slaw, then you can pack up a nutty chicken salad for a satisfying lunch. Extra delicious!

